<subSubSection id="5EEE652AFFCAFFFFFF05F90139C5F8DC" pageId="21" pageNumber="196" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="164B36A1FFCAFFFFFF05F90139C5F8DC" blockId="21.[136,1452,1742,1877]" pageId="21" pageNumber="196">
<emphasis id="2480EAB3FFCAFFFFFF05F9013B8CF961" bold="true" box="[136,251,1742,1768]" pageId="21" pageNumber="196">Diagnosis</emphasis>
:—This species is most similar to 
<taxonomicName id="D1F44D22FFCAFFFFFD09F9003F91F961" authority="Sobral &amp; M. A. D. Souza (2015: 222)" authorityName="Sobral &amp; M. A. D. Souza" authorityPageNumber="222" authorityYear="2015" box="[644,1254,1742,1769]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="21" pageNumber="196" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maarana">
<emphasis id="2480EAB3FFCAFFFFFD09F9003836F961" box="[644,833,1743,1768]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="196">Myrcia maarana</emphasis>
Sobral &amp; M.A.D.Souza (2015: 222)
</taxonomicName>
, from which it is distinguished by having leaf blades with one marginal vein (versus two marginal veins in 
<taxonomicName id="D1F44D22FFCAFFFFFBF9F93C3F88F885" authorityName="Sobral &amp; M. A. D. Souza" authorityYear="2015" box="[1140,1279,1779,1804]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="21" pageNumber="196" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maarana">
<emphasis id="2480EAB3FFCAFFFFFBF9F93C3F88F885" box="[1140,1279,1779,1804]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="196">M. maarana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), inflorescence moderately pubescent with light golden tricomes (vs. glabrous or with sparse reddish tricomes), flowers pentamerous (vs. tetramerous), and fruits ellipsoid (vs. oblate).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption id="428B6629FFC9FFFCFF05F8083859F7AD" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5424031" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5424031" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5424031/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="197" startId="22.[136,229,1991,2013]" targetBox="[157,1431,192,1966]" targetPageId="22">
